reviewText: Three Full Moon movies on three discs are for one price and saves money on not buying them piece by piece and I love Full Moon and their B-Movie quality!

This three pack of dvds from Full Moon studios. It includes Dark Angel the Ascent a movie about a demoness who escapes hell to earth to fight evil. Next up is Talisman a movie about a evil angel sent to destroy mankind. A fun movie. Last up is Demonicus. A movie about a man who is possessed by a demon gladiator and goes on a killing spree. If you a fan of horror this set is a must own.
